descript.abstract:
This dataset represents Massachusetts Bay Transportation Authority (MBTA) bus routes. The layer was developed by the Central Transportation Planning Staff (CTPS) and includes the many local variations during the course of a day along each primary route, such as a short turn or a spur into a shopping center.
The layer is named MBTABUSROUTES_ARC. It may be linked to the MBTA Bus Stops layer (see MBTABUSSTOPS_PT).
